{
  "stem": "4693.1",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Like in the families, not everybody was good with everybody else, you know.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "My mother was much younger than her elder part of the family.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "To those degrees where there are-- that she had nephews and nieces were older than her.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And-- but she was very well liked by all of them.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "She didn't have arguments with any one of them particularly.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And so we had quite a bit of entertaining at home.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And the members of family were coming as well.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And it was another type of entertainment that we have here, because they were mostly dinners.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We didn't have this, what we have here, parties or something.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "This was unknown.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "This started appearing in Poland only shortly before the Second World War.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I was very close particularly with one of my uncles, who was a very accomplished sportsman.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Before the First World War, he was taking prizes on bicycles, later in gymkhanas and horses.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And after the war, he was a very accomplished motorcar driver.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And from him I learned driving.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I took as a later on part in trials, country trials with him-- with him driving and me acting as an observer.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Otherwise, [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] my cousins, first cousins were all much older  than I was.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "So I was rather friendly with their children-- with their children, who were older than me on my age.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "I-- when I came to the-- close to the matriculation, the problem became what to do.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "I was very pessimistic as far as the future in Poland.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
